signature: Subscriber<? super T> call(Subscriber<? super T>)

enhanced_by.reason: The onStart method must be invoked before the call method to ensure the request for data is made.
The onNext method is invoked during the call method to add elements to the queue.
Both call and onCompleted methods handle the completion of data processing and subscription.
Both call and onError methods handle errors and ensure the child subscriber is notified.
